#: main/templates/main/about.html:5 main/templates/main/base.html:321
msgid "About Us"
msgstr "À propos de nous"

#: main/templates/main/about.html:311
msgid "About SolutionsTestLab"
msgstr "À propos de SolutionsTestLab"

#: main/templates/main/about.html:314
#| msgid ""
#| "SolutionsTestLab is a Quality Assurance, Software Testing and Test "
#| "Management company committed to delivering reliable, secure, and scalable "
#| "software solutions."
msgid ""
"SolutionsTestLab is a specialized Quality Assurance, Software Testing, and "
"Test Management company committed to delivering reliable, secure, and "
"scalable software solutions."
msgstr ""
"SolutionsTestLab est une entreprise spécialisée dans l’assurance qualité, "
"les tests logiciels et la gestion des tests, engagée à fournir des solutions "
"logicielles fiables, sécurisées et évolutives."

#: main/templates/main/about.html:318
msgid ""
"Our team of qualified Software Testers, Quality Assurance Engineers, Test "
"Analysts, and QA Consultants combines technical expertise with industry best "
"practices to help organizations achieve measurable improvements in software "
"quality."
msgstr ""
"Notre équipe de testeurs logiciels qualifiés, d’ingénieurs assurance "
"qualité, d’analystes de test et de consultants QA combine expertise "
"technique et meilleures pratiques du secteur afin d’aider les organisations "
"à obtenir des améliorations mesurables de la qualité logicielle."

#: main/templates/main/about.html:322
#| msgid ""
#| "We help companies prevent costly software failures by identifying hidden "
#| "defects, improving system reliability, and strengthening quality across "
#| "the full software lifecycle."
msgid ""
"We help companies prevent costly software failures by identifying hidden "
"defects, improving system reliability, reducing operational risk, and "
"strengthening quality throughout the entire software development lifecycle."
msgstr ""
"Nous aidons les entreprises à éviter les défaillances logicielles coûteuses "
"en identifiant les défauts cachés, en améliorant la fiabilité des systèmes, "
"en réduisant les risques opérationnels et en renforçant la qualité tout au "
"long du cycle de développement logiciel."

#: main/templates/main/about.html:325
msgid "Our Mission"
msgstr "Notre mission"

#: main/templates/main/about.html:328
msgid ""
"To help businesses release software with confidence through precision-driven "
"testing, reliable development practices, and quality assurance expertise."
msgstr ""
"Aider les entreprises à publier des logiciels en toute confiance grâce à des "
"tests précis, des pratiques de développement fiables et une expertise en "
"assurance qualité."

#: main/templates/main/about.html:331
msgid "Leadership Team"
msgstr "Équipe de direction"

#: main/templates/main/about.html:346
msgid "Managing Director & Founder"
msgstr "Directeur général et fondateur"

#: main/templates/main/about.html:350
msgid ""
"Gilbert Esambili Akeh is an experienced Software Engineer with a strong "
"track record of delivering reliable, secure, and scalable software "
"solutions. His expertise spans the entire Software Development Lifecycle, "
"combining software engineering, quality assurance, and DevOps practices to "
"help organizations build high-performing digital products."
msgstr ""
"Gilbert Esambili Akeh est un ingénieur logiciel expérimenté, reconnu pour la "
"livraison de solutions logicielles fiables, sécurisées et évolutives. Son "
"expertise couvre l’ensemble du cycle de développement logiciel, combinant "
"ingénierie logicielle, assurance qualité et pratiques DevOps afin d’aider "
"les organisations à créer des produits numériques performants."

#: main/templates/main/about.html:354
msgid ""
"As a Certified Python Programmer and skilled DevOps Engineer, Gilbert "
"specializes in software quality, automation, CI/CD pipeline optimization, "
"and modern development practices. His focus is on ensuring that software is "
"not only innovative but also maintainable, stable, and production-ready."
msgstr ""
"En tant que programmeur Python certifié et ingénieur DevOps expérimenté, "
"Gilbert est spécialisé dans la qualité logicielle, l’automatisation, "
"l’optimisation des pipelines CI/CD et les pratiques modernes de "
"développement. Son objectif est de garantir que les logiciels soient non "
"seulement innovants, mais aussi maintenables, stables et prêts pour la "
"production."

#: main/templates/main/about.html:358
msgid ""
"By bridging the gap between development, testing, and operations, he helps "
"organizations accelerate delivery while maintaining high standards of "
"quality, security, and operational excellence."
msgstr ""
"En reliant le développement, les tests et les opérations, il aide les "
"organisations à accélérer leurs livraisons tout en maintenant des standards "
"élevés de qualité, de sécurité et d’excellence opérationnelle."

#: main/templates/main/about.html:374
msgid "Managing Director"
msgstr "Directeur général"

#: main/templates/main/about.html:378
msgid ""
"Jan Wolfgang Sickinger has been active in software testing and quality "
"assurance since 2007. Throughout his career, he has worked as a Test Analyst "
"and Test Consultant on national and international projects for leading "
"consulting firms across the public sector, telecommunications, "
"manufacturing, and healthcare industries."
msgstr ""
"Jan Wolfgang Sickinger travaille dans le domaine des tests logiciels et de "
"l’assurance qualité depuis 2007. Au cours de sa carrière, il a travaillé "
"comme Test Analyst et Test Consultant sur des projets nationaux et "
"internationaux pour de grandes sociétés de conseil dans les secteurs public, "
"des télécommunications, de l’industrie manufacturière et de la santé."

#: main/templates/main/about.html:382
msgid ""
"His expertise lies in analysing, structuring, and continuously improving "
"testing processes to achieve measurable increases in software quality. "
"Through his extensive practical experience and methodological expertise, he "
"helps organizations establish sustainable quality assurance frameworks."
msgstr ""
"Son expertise consiste à analyser, structurer et améliorer continuellement "
"les processus de test afin d’obtenir des améliorations mesurables de la "
"qualité logicielle. Grâce à sa vaste expérience pratique et à son expertise "
"méthodologique, il aide les organisations à mettre en place des cadres "
"durables d’assurance qualité."

#: main/templates/main/about.html:386
msgid ""
"Jan holds multiple ISTQB certifications and is also certified in "
